      "Cannabis concentrates represent one of the fastest-growing segments of the market, and for good reason. By isolating the plant's most desirable compounds, concentrates deliver intensified flavors, aromas, and potency in a remarkably efficient format. But walking into a dispensary and seeing terms like shatter, wax, budder, live resin, rosin, and diamonds can feel like learning a new language. The good news is that once you understand the basic categories, navigating concentrates becomes straightforward and even fun.",
